Titolo: Code: Realize − Guardian of Rebirth

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Code: Realize − Guardian of Rebirth is an otome visual novel video game developed by Otomate for PlayStation Vita, released in 2014 in Japan and in 2015 in North America and Europe. The game features a steampunk aesthetic and a cast of literary and historical figures, including Arsène Lupin, Abraham Van Helsing, Victor Frankenstein, Impey Barbicane, and Count Saint-Germain. A fan disc, Code: Realize − Future Blessings, was released on November 26, 2016. Aksys Games localized both games in English. A second fan disc, Code: Realize − Shirogane no Kiseki will be released for PlayStation 4 and PlayStation Vita in Japan. An anime television series adaptation by M.S.C aired from October 7 to December 23, 2017.

Genere: Visual novel

Valutazione: 84
